{"tid":722104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：美國執意發動貿易戰，中國奉陪到底","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T00:09:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"851819bb4c10c5bbbbdcceed24be7b92ebc9420a","tid":722104,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://linepost.hk/images/foreignmin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Fimages%2Fforeignmin.jpg&h=1f985e18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽回應美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅指，與中國就貿易糾紛進行的多輪談判並無進展，又認為中國會較美國輸得更多的言論，強調中方不挑貿易戰，但不怕貿易戰，認為在解決經貿問題上對話比對抗強，但如果有人執意發起貿易戰，中方會堅決維護自身的正當合法權益，奉陪到底。<br />\n<br />\n對於中方會否再美方就經貿問題再展開談判，及國家副主席王歧山會否赴美，耿爽重申，中方主張雙方通過對話協商解決有關經貿問題，指中美之前三次磋商取得一些進展，希望美方注意到中方在過程中展示出充分誠意和善意。耿爽並沒有回應中國會否再主持同美國的磋商，亦無回應國家副主席王岐山會否在新關稅措施實施前，與美國談判。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/1961-d20180620-98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F1961-d20180620-98&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c63eff98\" target=\"_blank\">http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/1961-d20180620-98</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde2fa0bd57aa890cf7f01c54773e807c6f4ac6c","tid":722104,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47f4b688035fe341e11ceef9e4b4c9869740e8b","tid":722104,"uid":147586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"中國人是大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa88ee84a5d28e6245a5add912b9b8644bff8f25","tid":722104,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB